metadata.name: Marina
metadata.description:
This is my self portrait.
I will start this NFT collection with my photo and as a photographer I will tell you my opinion about femininity. 

Femininity is harmony, naturalness and sensuality. it's hiding somewhere inside. I think every women understands what I'm talking about. Real femininity is not being afraid to be funny, maybe stupid or naive. Don't be afraid to be yourself and just keep shining.
